        <: td() :>For the shadow style, the x and y offsets of the shadow.
    <:TR():><: td() :>$pango_markup
        <: td() :>$pango_markup
        <: td() :>Indicates that the text should be interpreted as a pango markup string. See: http://developer.gnome.org/pango/stable/PangoMarkupFormat.html
